		</font>
		<hr size="1">Ok...using macros....</P><P>All this really is is a series of commands in a certain order to get a desired effect.</P><P>For example....</P><P>On the bard, you may have targeted a Mob_1.</P><P>On the wiz, you might set up a macro....<BR>(Make sure to have /autoassist off )</P><P>/stand<BR>/tar Bard<BR>/assist<BR>/pause 100<BR>/cast (number equal to snare)</P><P>Then a second hotkey something like </P><P>/cast (nuke number)<BR>/pause 40<BR>/sit</P><P><BR>That way you really only need to switch to the wizard twice per fight.</P><P>~ Lan<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
	</font>
