		<hr size="1">it is a challange 2 boxing with both the wiz and bard.  interesting, and i have to pay attention or things go south real fast.</P><P>using wiz snare for a few reasons.  1.  to keep up some of his casting skills as he levels.</P><P>2.  it is easier to use his snare so i can use my better slow attack and reduce the AC, vs just snare and slow attack.</P><P>i like using bind over chains for the AC debuffer as well as the slow.  so i let wiz snare so bard can focus on slow, haste, and DS.  have not twisted in DoTs as i find the DS works well so far for me.</P><P><BR>interesting charming with the bard, and wiz combo too.  scary when i miss the recharm, and have 2 red mobs come flying at me.</P><P></P><P><BR><hr><font style=font-size:8pt color=yellow>*Worlds worst speller*<BR><font color=yellow><BR>"For those who believe, then no proof is needed.  For those who are skeptics, then no proof will suffice."<font color=00FFFF><BR>"Pigs get fat, but Hogs get slaughtered and VI is a big HOG."<BR><font color=yellow> "So, reading some of my posts is sort of like having sex in your parents house???"  Dr. Zin</P><P></font><BR><br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
