		</font>
		<hr size="1">When using pauses in hot keys I feel its always a good idea to "double cast" the spell before the pause goes into effect something like this;</P><P>/stand<BR>/tar Bard<BR>/assist<BR>/pause 2 /cast #X<BR>/pause 100 /cast #X<BR>/sit</P><P>That way if the first cast fizzles the second cast will still go off without making you wait for the pause to complete.  But if the first cast doesn't fizzle your second command to cast will do nothing.</P><P>Just my two bits for something your most likely already aware of. <img src='http://www.everlore.com/gimages/smile.gif' width=15 height=15 align=middle> <br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
	</font>
